parameters: Why are you so damn persistent!
Just because you’ve managed to clear some
of the simple obstacles I’ve placed in your
way doesn’t mean you’re anything special!
I’ll just have to take you down myself!
Impossible... How did you manage to beat me
when I have such powerful dark magic on
It’s unfair how gifted you are...
I don’t think I’m very gifted. I just had
a goal set, to save my friends.
Go into the next room and you'll find
your friends there. Go and save them.
